&lt;p&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Director, Regional Sales&lt;/strong&gt; will be responsible for defining, evolving, and executing the regional go-to-market strategy, with a primary focus on accelerating net-new business growth across our Enterprise accounts. In this role, you will provide strategic leadership, operational excellence, and sales management support to a high-performing team of senior sales representatives, while heavily leveraging and building standardized sales playbooks to scale success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What your impact will be…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive New Logo Acquisition:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop and execute a sophisticated regional sales strategy to consistently meet and exceed net-new customer acquisition targets, driving predictable revenue growth and market share expansion within your territory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Playbook Development &amp;amp; Execution:&lt;/strong&gt; Design, implement, and institutionalize scalable sales playbooks, ensuring the team has a standardized blueprint for hunting, qualifying, and closing net-new enterprise logos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Excellence &amp;amp; Forecasting:&lt;/strong&gt; Establish a rigorous pipeline management, forecasting cadence, and performance expectation framework to ensure every sales representative achieves and exceeds their goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Account Penetration:&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure representatives have a deep understanding of their prospects and are leveraging all corporate resources to &quot;Know Your Customer&quot; (KYC), with a laser focus on deeply penetrating the region&#39;s Top 10 target accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High-Performance Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Build, mentor, and maintain a world-class sales team. Provide hands-on coaching, strategic deal support, and professional development to maximize individual and collective revenue generation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Market Awareness &amp;amp; Value Selling:&lt;/strong&gt; Expand brand awareness of the product portfolio within the territory, building a sustainable, high-velocity pipeline rooted in quantifying and delivering tangible business value.&lt;/li&gt;
