&lt;li&gt;Strategic Guidance: Serve as an involved leader who takes an active role in the team&#39;s daily success and long-term career growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Sales Strategy &amp;amp; Operations&lt;/h4&gt;
