&lt;li&gt;Revenue Growth: Lead a multi-product sales strategy and manage an integrated go-to-market approach for Australia &amp;amp; New Zealand in collaboration with EDB cross-functional teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Forecasting &amp;amp; Analysis: Manage and report on projected targets, forecasts, and results. Provide in-depth market research and competitive analysis to executive leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaboration: Work closely with Marketing, Operations, and Services teams to develop holistic regional strategies centred on value-selling, bundling, and upselling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
